message.content: <OUTPUT_TEXT>To effectively contact customers regarding inquiries or claim investigation results, ensure you have all necessary information about the customer's case. Begin by reviewing the details of their inquiry or claim, and prepare clear and concise information about the investigation results or any planned adjustments. When reaching out, use a polite and professional tone, and be ready to answer any questions they may have. It's important to provide reassurance and support, ensuring the customer feels valued and informed throughout the process.</OUTPUT_TEXT>
